item.title: First Post
item.description: Hi! This is my first post on my personal blog where I will be sharing my thoughts about programming, learning, and technology!

About Me Hi! My name is Jayde. I am a recent Computer Science graduate from the University of Manitoba and an aspiring Full Stack Developer. In my studies I have specialized in Software Development and Human Computer Interaction. Outside of my studies, I am a University athelete, gamer, and movie-nerd!
